race.comment: SOURCE OF DELIGHT (10) was quickly back on track beaten a whisker at Kyneton over this distance. Was a touch unlucky and with the race fitness she will be tough to beat. TEXTURE (8) resumes and on what we've seen he can threaten. Won a recent jumpout and Rawiller rides from an inside barrier. LEFT ON READ (2) came off an injury enforced break at Wangaratta and will be better for it. Showed some ability early doors and he has each way claims with the extra fitness. CARNIVAL RICHES (17) has the inside barrier, a 2kg claim and the blinkers on for the first time. We are likely to see improvement from her.
